      "updated": 1714000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "LEGEND  \u25a2 red=middleware  \u25a2 blue=page (server)  \u25a2 orange=client component\n\u25a2 green=hook  \u25a2 purple=server action  \u25a2 pink=API route  \u25a2 peach=AI lib\n\u25a2 gray=util/lib  \u25a2 teal=i18n  \u25a2 cyan=external service  \u25a2 yellow=user/browser\n\u2192 data flow / call.   Read top-to-bottom: request \u2192 middleware \u2192 page \u2192 UI \u2192 hooks \u2192 server.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LEGEND  \u25a2 red=middleware  \u25a2 blue=page (server)  \u25a2 orange=client component\n\u25a2 green=hook  \u25a2 purple=server action  \u25a2 pink=API route  \u25a2 peach=AI lib\n\u25a2 gray=util/lib  \u25a2 teal=i18n  \u25a2 cyan=external service  \u25a2 yellow=user/browser\n\u2192 data flow / call.   Read top-to-bottom: request \u2192 middleware \u2192 page \u2192 UI \u2192 hooks \u2192 server.",
