      "text": "src/components/features/landing/* (12)\nALL SERVER COMPONENTS (getTranslations)\n\n\u2022 hero.tsx \u2014 title + CTA + TerminalAnimation\n\u2022 terminal-animation.tsx \u2014 fake CLI (270 lines, SVG/CSS)\n\u2022 problem-statement.tsx \u2014 ChatGPT vs DevMentor\n\u2022 how-it-works.tsx \u2014 3 steps\n\u2022 core-features.tsx \u2014 4 cards\n\u2022 supported-tracks.tsx \u2014 animated SVG circuit\n\u2022 use-cases.tsx \u2014 3 personas\n\u2022 live-preview.tsx \u2014 fake browser chrome\n\u2022 faq.tsx \u2014 6 Qs\n\u2022 final-cta.tsx \u2014 closing CTA\n\u2022 footer.tsx \u2014 links + credits\n\u2022 section-heading.tsx \u2014 shared <h2>\n\nNo client state. No data. Pure copy from\nmessages/ar.json + en.json + CSS keyframes.",
