      "updated": 1714000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ChatSessionPanel INNER (key={panelKey})\nDeclared inside chat-area.tsx\nRefs: messagesEndRef, messagesContainerRef,\n  inputRef, isNearBottomRef,\n  persistedSessionIdRef, sendLockRef\nUses useChat({api,initialMessages,onError,onFinish})\n  + useChatSession(userId, selectedSessionId)\n\u2022 handleSend(): ensure session (createSession\n  if needed) \u2192 save user msg \u2192 updateTitleAction\n  if first msg \u2192 handleSubmit (stream)\n\u2022 onFinish(message): saveChatMessageAction\n  (assistant) \u2192 onSessionsRefresh()\n\u2022 handleScroll: distFromBottom<120 ? sticky\n\u2022 handleFilesSelected: addAttachmentsFromFileList\n  \u2192 3 error codes (too_many|too_large|type_not_allowed)\nEffect: scrollIntoView when near bottom\nEffect: derive currentTitle from first user msg (40c)\nUI: <WelcomeScreen> if 0 msgs else list of\n  <MessageBubble> + <TypingIndicator>;\n  always <ChatInput ref/>",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ChatSessionPanel INNER (key={panelKey})\nDeclared inside chat-area.tsx\nRefs: messagesEndRef, messagesContainerRef,\n  inputRef, isNearBottomRef,\n  persistedSessionIdRef, sendLockRef\nUses useChat({api,initialMessages,onError,onFinish})\n  + useChatSession(userId, selectedSessionId)\n\u2022 handleSend(): ensure session (createSession\n  if needed) \u2192 save user msg \u2192 updateTitleAction\n  if first msg \u2192 handleSubmit (stream)\n\u2022 onFinish(message): saveChatMessageAction\n  (assistant) \u2192 onSessionsRefresh()\n\u2022 handleScroll: distFromBottom<120 ? sticky\n\u2022 handleFilesSelected: addAttachmentsFromFileList\n  \u2192 3 error codes (too_many|too_large|type_not_allowed)\nEffect: scrollIntoView when near bottom\nEffect: derive currentTitle from first user msg (40c)\nUI: <WelcomeScreen> if 0 msgs else list of\n  <MessageBubble> + <TypingIndicator>;\n  always <ChatInput ref/>",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false
    },
