      "text": "MessageBubble (router) + sub-components\nchat/_components/message-bubble.tsx\nMessageBubble({message}) \u2192 switches on role\n\n\u2022 UserBubble \u2014 cyan tint, right-aligned;\n   shows text + image previews + file links\n   (truncated) with mediaType label\n\u2022 AssistantBubble \u2014 left-aligned, hex avatar;\n   <ReactMarkdown components={...}> with\n   custom code/p/ul/ol/li/h1-h3/blockquote/a\n\u2022 CodeBlock(language, children) \u2014\n   header (lang label + copy button)\n   + Prism oneDark SyntaxHighlighter\n   + state copied + 2s reset\n\u2022 TypingIndicator (export) \u2014\n   3 cyan dots (animate-bounce, 0/150/300ms)",
