      "text": "useChatSession (HOOK)\nsrc/hooks/chat/use-chat-session.ts\nProps: userId, initialSessionId\nState: sessionId (synced via useEffect\n  when initialSessionId changes)\nReturns: {sessionId, setSessionId,\n  createSession}\nFns:\n\u2022 createSession(title) \u2192\n   createChatSessionAction({userId,title})\n   \u2192 setSessionId(s.id) \u2192 returns s.id\n\u2022 If no userId: throws 'No user id'",
      "fontSize": 11,
