      "updated": 1714000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GET /api/auth/callback  \u2192  route.ts\nsrc/app/api/auth/callback/route.ts\nOAuth redirect target.\n\u2022 reads ?code, ?next from URL\n\u2022 localeFromNextParam(next)\n\u2022 safeNextPath(next, locale)\n\u2022 createClient() (server) +\n   exchangeCodeForSession(code)\n\u2022 On success \u2192 302 to <origin><next>\n\u2022 On error \u2192 302 to /[locale]/login?\n   error=auth_failed&next=<next>",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "r-apicb",
      "originalText": "GET /api/auth/callback  \u2192  route.ts\nsrc/app/api/auth/callback/route.ts\nOAuth redirect target.\n\u2022 reads ?code, ?next from URL\n\u2022 localeFromNextParam(next)\n\u2022 safeNextPath(next, locale)\n\u2022 createClient() (server) +\n   exchangeCodeForSession(code)\n\u2022 On success \u2192 302 to <origin><next>\n\u2022 On error \u2192 302 to /[locale]/login?\n   error=auth_failed&next=<next>",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false
    },
