      "text": "SERVICE LAYER\nsrc/lib/services/chat.service.ts\nPure data access \u2014 actions call this\nwith an already-created Supabase client.\n\u2022 getChatSessions(supabase, userId)\n   SELECT * WHERE user_id=?\n   ORDER BY updated_at DESC\n\u2022 getChatMessages(supabase, sessionId)\n   SELECT * WHERE session_id=?\n   ORDER BY created_at ASC",
      "fontSize": 11,
