      "text": "AI PROMPTS\nsrc/lib/ai/prompts.ts\n\n\u2022 MENTOR_SYSTEM_PROMPT (active)\n   English DevMentor persona, code-first\n   answers, MD code blocks. (Arabic\n   variant currently commented out.)\n\n\u2022 CODE_REVIEW_SYSTEM_PROMPT\n   For /review feature (planned).\n\n\u2022 RAG_SYSTEM_PROMPT(context)\n   Will be used by RAG feature next \u2014\n   wraps retrieved context.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "r-prompts",
      "originalText": "AI PROMPTS\nsrc/lib/ai/prompts.ts\n\n\u2022 MENTOR_SYSTEM_PROMPT (active)\n   English DevMentor persona, code-first\n   answers, MD code blocks. (Arabic\n   variant currently commented out.)\n\n\u2022 CODE_REVIEW_SYSTEM_PROMPT\n   For /review feature (planned).\n\n\u2022 RAG_SYSTEM_PROMPT(context)\n   Will be used by RAG feature next \u2014\n   wraps retrieved context.",
