      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1714000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "NORMALIZE UI MSGS\nsrc/lib/ai/normalize-ui-messages-for-model.ts\nnormalizeUiMessagesForAttachmentCapabilities(\n  messages, capabilityKey)\n\u2022 For each message.parts of type 'file':\n   - if image and !supportsImage \u2192 drop +\n     append [image attachment removed] note\n   - if non-image and !supportsNon-Image \u2192\n     drop + append [file attachment removed]\n   - else keep as-is\n\u2022 Used inside /api/chat before\n   convertToModelMessages so Groq Llama\n   never sees unsupported file parts.\nDepends on getModelAttachmentCapabilities(key).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "r-norm",
      "originalText": "NORMALIZE UI MSGS\nsrc/lib/ai/normalize-ui-messages-for-model.ts\nnormalizeUiMessagesForAttachmentCapabilities(\n  messages, capabilityKey)\n\u2022 For each message.parts of type 'file':\n   - if image and !supportsImage \u2192 drop +\n     append [image attachment removed] note\n   - if non-image and !supportsNon-Image \u2192\n     drop + append [file attachment removed]\n   - else keep as-is\n\u2022 Used inside /api/chat before\n   convertToModelMessages so Groq Llama\n   never sees unsupported file parts.\nDepends on getModelAttachmentCapabilities(key).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false
    },
