      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MODEL CAPABILITIES\nsrc/lib/ai/model-capabilities.ts\ngetModelAttachmentCapabilities(key)\n\u2192 {supportsImageInput, supportsNonImageInput}\n\nMap of CapabilityKey \u2192 flags.\n'groq-llama-3.3-70b' \u2192 {image:false, non:false}\n'gemini-2.5-flash' \u2192 {image:true, non:true}\nFallback: both false (safest).\nKey is read from CHAT_MODEL_CAPABILITY_KEY.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "r-modelcap",
      "originalText": "MODEL CAPABILITIES\nsrc/lib/ai/model-capabilities.ts\ngetModelAttachmentCapabilities(key)\n\u2192 {supportsImageInput, supportsNonImageInput}\n\nMap of CapabilityKey \u2192 flags.\n'groq-llama-3.3-70b' \u2192 {image:false, non:false}\n'gemini-2.5-flash' \u2192 {image:true, non:true}\nFallback: both false (safest).\nKey is read from CHAT_MODEL_CAPABILITY_KEY.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": false
    },
