      "text": "AUTH UTILS\nsrc/lib/auth/safe-next-path.ts\n\u2022 safeNextPath(next, locale) \u2014 open-redirect\n   guard: must start with /<locale>/, no //, no\n   protocol; otherwise returns defaultChatPath\n\u2022 localeFromNextParam(next) \u2014 extracts ar|en\n   from path, default 'ar'\n\u2022 defaultChatPath(locale) \u2192 `/${locale}/chat`\nUsed by: proxy.ts, /login page, /api/auth/callback,\n   useGoogleLogin (computes redirectTo).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": "r-safe",
      "originalText": "AUTH UTILS\nsrc/lib/auth/safe-next-path.ts\n\u2022 safeNextPath(next, locale) \u2014 open-redirect\n   guard: must start with /<locale>/, no //, no\n   protocol; otherwise returns defaultChatPath\n\u2022 localeFromNextParam(next) \u2014 extracts ar|en\n   from path, default 'ar'\n\u2022 defaultChatPath(locale) \u2192 `/${locale}/chat`\nUsed by: proxy.ts, /login page, /api/auth/callback,\n   useGoogleLogin (computes redirectTo).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
